The program is freely available and is provided as is.

The source code is freely available for compilation and building into
your analysis programs.  However, if you want to incorporate any part
of the source code into distributed software (free or for fee), please
contact the authors for permission.

The program is maintained at
http://biostat.mc.vanderbilt.edu/GWAsimulator

The paper associated with the program is
Li C, Li M (2007) GWAsimulator: A rapid whole genome simulation
program. Bioinformatics (in press).
